title: Dishwasher SENSOR

installationInstructions.author: Melvin from SACRAMENTO, KY
installationInstructions.title: would not shut off.
installationInstructions.content: easy the sensor was on the right side, and easy to get to,  I turn off the power, turned off the water, and pulled it out, the first thing I saw was the yellow wires and plug.  took about 5 minutes, to replace it.
